t date|2018|3|29}}\n |Viewers         = 5.86<ref name=\"1.03\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/thursday-final-ratings-march-29-2018/|title='Big Bang Theory,' 'Grey's Anatomy' and 'Chicago Fire' adjust up, 'SWAT' adjusts down: Thursday final ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|website=[[TV by the Numbers]]|date=March 30, 2018|accessdate=March 30, 2018}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    = The team responds to the house fire at JJ's apartment with Dean risking his life to save Seth, who ends up dying at the hospital. An emotional JJ visits Dean at the station to help her process the loss. After a disagreement between Jack and Andy on the scene, Frankel calls them both out on their mistakes and later shows her respect for Jack because he, unlike Andy, had to work his way up without connections. Andy overhears this but leaves before Jack tells Frankel that if anything, Andy's father held her back. Maya and Travis pick sides for the Captain position. Ben finds it difficult not to have a follow-up with the people they rescue. Pruitt has a hard time staying at home and ends up returning to the station for administrative duties while Ryan wonders if Andy still sees him as his teenage self like her father does.\n |LineColor       = 9F938F\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 4\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n |Title           = Reignited\n |DirectedBy      = [[Dennis Smith (director)|Dennis Smith]]\n |WrittenBy       = Ilene Rosenzweig\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|4|5}}\n |Viewers         = 5.09<ref name=\"1.04\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/thursday-final-ratings-april-5-2018/|title='Big Bang Theory,' 'Grey's Anatomy' adjust up, 'Mom,' 'Supernatural,' 'Arrow' down: Thursday final ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|website=[[TV by the Numbers]]|date=April 6, 2018|accessdate=April 6, 2018}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    = The team deals with a fire at a brand-new bed-and-breakfast that keeps reigniting. Jack and Andy resume their 