iction\n| note2        = Inst.\n| length2      = 4:02\n| total_length = 8:04\n}}\n\n{{tracklist\n| extra_column= Artist\n| headline        = Disc 2:\n| title1      = Endless Run\n| note1       = Opening Title \n| extra1      = Oh Joon Sung\n| length1     = 2:31\n| title2      = Awaken Vampire\n| note2       = \n| extra2      = Oh Joon Sung\n| length2     = 2:49\n| title3      = Broken Door\n| note3       = \n| extra3      = Oh Joon Sung\n| length3     = 2:06\n| title4          = Brave Hand\n| note4           = \n| extra4          = Oh Joon Sung\n| length4         = 2:25\n| title5          = Black cloud\n| note5           = \n| extra5          = Oh Joon Sung\n| length5         = 2:22\n| title6          = Flying Hero\n| note6           = \n| extra6          = Oh Joon Sung\n| length6         = 2:11\n| title7          = Hidden Heart\n| note7           = \n| extra7          = Oh Joon Sung\n| length7         = 2:29\n| title8          = Hot Tension \n| note8           = \n| extra8          = Oh Joon Sung\n| length8         = 2:10\n| title9          = I am a Prince\n| note9           = \n| extra9          = Oh Joon Sung\n| length9         = 2:02\n| title10     = In the forest\n| note10      = \n| extra10     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length10    = 1:58\n| title11        = Inside Fighter\n| note11         = \n| extra11        = Oh Joon Sung\n| length11       = 1:58\n| title12     = Keep the Faith\n| note12      = \n| extra12     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length12    = 2:18\n| title13         = Morning Dew\n| note13          = \n| extra13         = Oh Joon Sung\n| length13        = 3:02\n| title14    = Night World\n| note14     = \n| extra14    = Oh Joon Sung\n| length14   = 2:30\n| title15    = Old Rival\n| note15     =\n| extra15    = Oh Joon Sung\n| length15   = 2:18\n| title16     = Sadness of Vampire\n| note16      =\n| extra16     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length16    = 2:45\n| title17     = Trans-Vampire\n| note17      = \n| extra17     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length17    = 2:12\n| title18     = Too Fast\n| note18      =\n| extra18     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length18    = 2:28\n| title19     = The Dark Palace\n| note19      =\n| extra19     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length19    = 2:04\n| title20     = Tears of the flower\n| note20      =\n| extra20     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length20    = 2:34\n| title21     = Unbroken\n| note21      =\n| extra21     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length21    = 2:21\n| title22     = Wait for you\n| note22      =\n| extra22     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length22    = 1:59\n| title23     = Walk a Night\n| note23      =\n| extra23     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length23    = 1:34\n| title24     = Where are you going? \n| note24      =\n| extra24     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length24    = 2:29\n| title25     = Waltz of Memory\n| note25      =\n| extra25     = Oh Joon Sung\n| length25    = 2:37\n}}\n\n==Ratings==\n{|class=wikitable\n|-align=center\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Episode\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Broadcast date\n!colspan=\"2\"|TNmS ratings<ref>[http://www.tnms.tv/rating/default.asp TNmS Daily Ratings: this links to current day-select the date from drop down menu] in Korean</ref>\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[Nielsen Corporation|AGB Nielsen]] ratings<ref>[http://www.agbnielsen.co.kr/index.asp?ref=0 AGB Daily Ratings: this links to current day-select the date from drop down menu] in Korean</ref>\n|-\n!Nationwide\n![[Seoul Capital Area]]\n!Nationwide\n![[Seoul Capital Area]]\n|-align=center\n!1\n|July 8, 2015\n|{{color|red|'''7.4%'''}}\n|{{color|red|'''9.1%'''}}\n|7.7%\n|8.1%\n|-align=center\n!2\n|July 9, 2015\n|6.8%\n|8.9%\n|6.8%\n|7.3%\n|-align=center\n!3\n|July 15, 2015\n|7.2%\n|{{color|red|'''9.1%'''}}\n|7.7%\n|7.8%\n|-\n|-align=center\n!4\n|July 16, 2015\n|7.1%\n|8.2%\n|7.7%\n|8.5%\n|-\n|-align=center\n!5\n|July 22, 2015\n|7.3%\n|9.0%\n|7.8%\n|{{color|red|'''8.9%'''}}\n|-\n|-align=center\n!6\n|July 23, 2015\n|6.4%\n|7.5%\n|7.9%\n|8.7%\n|-\n|-align=center\n!7\n|July 29, 2015\n|6.9%\n|8.0%\n|7.9%\n|8.3%\n|-\n|-align=center\n!8\n|July 30, 2015\n|7.3%\n|7.9%\n|7.4%\n|7.8%\n|-\n|-align=center\n!9\n|August 5, 